vote.title: Authorize an amendment to an existing lease agreement with Martin Luther King, Jr. Family Health Clinic doing business as Foremost Family Health Centers to extend the lease agreement for an additional five years for approximately 25,247 square feet of office and clinic space located at 2922 Martin Luther King, Jr. Boulevard, Building B to be used as a family health and wellness facility for the period July 1, 2025 through June 30, 2030 - Estimated Revenue: General Fund $180,000.00
